HEADWORD: Orthotone
<hw>Or"tho*tone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ortho-</ets>
+ Gr. <?/ tone, accent.]</ety> <fld>(Gr. Gram.)</fld> <def>Retaining the
